I had a HELL of a time finding one a few months ago,
when I was in desperate need of one.  I was told that
the after-market ones were............er........lacking in quality.
I wound up getting a used, but worn, one from Ken at
The Bus Co., and having the worn surfaces built up with
weld, and reground to new spec.  Gene Berg has the
bushing kits.

